<PillHeading Headtitle="Our History" variant="green"/>
</div>
<p class="headfont center">Better Website Means A User Experience</p>
<p class="brødtekst center">Ippsum is the result of synergy between our teams and our customers. Our company culture is focused on excellent productivity, customer satisfaction, respect for team and individual achievements.</p>
 <Image class="videomid" src={VideoCenter} alt="gruppe af mennesker video" />
</article>
<section class="full">
<PillHeading Headtitle="Our Team" variant="yellow"/>
